直到1909年前，[[自然歷史|自然歷史學家]]透過[[大臼齒|大臼齒]]樣式的相似性將河馬與[[豬|豬]]分類為同一群。然而諸多證據，包括[[血液|血液]][[蛋白質|蛋白質]]、[[分子系統發生學|分子系統發生學]]<ref name="Genomes">{{Cite journal|title = Analyses of mitochondrial genomes strongly support a hippopotamus-whale clade|volume = 265|issue = 1412|year = 1998|journal = [[皇家學會報告|皇家學會報告]]|pmid = 9881471|author = Ursing, B.M.|author2 = Arnason U.|pmc = 1689531|doi = 10.1098/rspb.1998.0567|pages = 2251–5}}</ref>、[[DNA|DNA]]<ref name="DNA">{{Cite journal|url = http://mbe.oxfordjournals.org/content/14/5/537.full.pdf|format = PDF|title = More DNA support for a Cetacea/Hippopotamidae clade: the blood-clotting protein gene gamma-fibrinogen|author = Gatesy, J.|journal = {{link-en|Molecular Biology and Evolution}}|date = 1 May 1997|volume = 14|pages = 537–543|pmid = 9159931|issue = 5|doi = 10.1093/oxfordjournals.molbev.a025790|access-date = 2018-11-15|archive-date = 2015-12-31|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151231230524/http://mbe.oxfordjournals.org/content/14/5/537.full.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Nature2009">{{Cite journal|title = Hippopotamus and whale phylogeny|author1=Geisler, J. H.  |author2=Theodor, J. M.|journal = [[Nature_(journal)|Nature]]|year = 2009|pmid = 19295550|volume = 458| doi = 10.1038/nature07776|issue = 7236|pages = E1–4; discussion E5}}</ref>與[[化石|化石]]紀錄，都顯示河馬現存關係親緣最近的類群為[[鯨豚類|鯨豚類]]<ref name="ScienceNews">{{cite web|first= Robert|last= Sanders|title = Scientists find missing link between the dolphin, whale and its closest relative, the hippo|date = 25 January 2005|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20150226060713/http://www.innovations-report.com//html/reports/life-sciences/report-39309.html|archivedate= 26 February 2015|deadurl= no|accessdate = 8 January 2011|url = http://www.innovations-report.com/html/reports/life_sciences/report-39309.html|work = Science News Daily}}</ref>。河馬與鯨豚的共同祖先自[[反芻亞目|反芻亞目]]分化，而在不久之後河馬與鯨豚也分別分化為兩個獨立的演化支<ref name="DNA"/><ref name="Cetartiodactyla">{{cite journal |author1=Boisserie, Jean-Renaud |author2=Lihoreau, Fabrice |author3=Brunet, Michel |year= 2005|title= The position of Hippopotamidae within Cetartiodactyla|journal= [[Proceedings_of_the_National_Academy_of_Sciences|Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences]] |volume= 102 |issue= 5|pages= 1537–1541|doi= 10.1073/pnas.0409518102|pmid= 15677331 |pmc=547867}}</ref>。

